data.fec.gov.title: Candidate Summary
data.fec.gov.description: This file contains information for each candidate who has registered with the FEC or appears on an official state ballot for an election to the U.S. House of Representatives, U.S. Senate or U.S. President. The table is available for the current election cycle and for election cycles through 2008.
